prHeadline: Canaan Releases Self-developed Edge AI Chip, the Kendryte K510
headlineTxt: Jul 08, 2021, 06:00 ETCanaan Releases Self-developed Edge AI Chip, the Kendryte K510Kendryte K510 chip is the result of two years of work by our R&D team to further innovative and optimize our core chip architecture. With upgraded machine vision and improved programming flexibility, the Kendryte K510 can better address the demands of mid- to high-end application scenarios.
